### ==================================================
### CONVERSATION ENDPOINTS
### ==================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Direct Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "DIRECT",
  "participantIds": ["user-id-of-other-person"]
}

### Create Group Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "GROUP",
  "participantIds": ["user-id-1", "user-id-2", "user-id-3"],
  "name": "Project Team",
  "description": "Team discussion for the new project",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/group-avatar.jpg"
}

### Get All My Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Conversation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/conversation-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
